        <h1 class="clear" itemprop="headline">Calais crisis: Migrants stay in British hotels at taxpayers' expense</h1>

        
        <p class="lead" class="clearfix">MIGRANTS who have smuggled themselves into the Britain from Calais are staying in hotels at the taxpayer's expense, it has been revealed.</p>

